{"tid":1849743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該實行限罩令？","createTime":"2020-01-29T08:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T08:18:39.000Z","uid":147317,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"081f7c7789dbd20caf4bd20b83825a086e891715","tid":1849743,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"相信咁多位手足都周圍搶緊口罩<br />\n<br />\n首先要多謝好多程班長同埋阿布盡力幫大家買口罩<br />\n同時我都知道好多人買唔到而家非常徬徨，既然供應一時之間唔能夠加強，咁就要徹底管控需求<br />\n<br />\n1.今日喺上水有好多大陸水貨客排隊買$5 一個口罩<br />\n2.過年期間大量人用高鐵同火車運口罩返大陸<br />\n3.網傳政府捐左20個貨櫃嘅口罩比大陸<br />\n<br />\n呢啲賤人全部都係同香港人搶口罩嘅仆街，完全當香港人唔係人。所以我認為政府必定要引用引用緊急法限制所有口罩出口。<br />\n<br />\n我建議，每個出境嘅人只能帶10個口罩，如果唔係就要坐監半年同罰錢50000<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足贊成？ 如果有其實可以發起一個藍絲加黃絲嘅大遊行，要突顯呢個政府幾咁冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時亦都要迫嗰啲非主流建制派表態，究竟支唔支持限罩"},{"pid":"5912664de2b15a80dcc3430978a329571d933a93","tid":1849743,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:03:09.000Z","msg":"我要同醫護一齊罷工"},{"pid":"5829146dee83e108aa8ad5d7f974c0349ac68620","tid":1849743,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Js5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=f2b5f084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockq